title: I Bedroom w/ Den - Walking distance to Large Park
posting_body: ['Welcome to Higby, modern apartments in Berkeley, CA.', 'Higby is a refined living experience in the heart of Historic Southwest Berkeley.', 'With studios, one-, two-, and three- bedroom homes and inviting common areas.', 'Higby creates a place that is both a home and a gathering space.', 'Walking distance from craft breweries, celebrated restaurants, organic markets and a wealth of cultural highlights.', 'Higby is a refined living experience that celebrates exploration and discovery.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 22', 'OR Text', '22', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'Interested In This Unit?', 'Use this link for more details:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom + 1 Den, 1 Bath, approximately 787 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Modern kitchens with custom fixtures', '- Full size, front-loading washers and dryers', '- Quartz countertops and full backsplashes', '- Energy Star-rated appliances', '- Private balconies in select units', '- Gas range cooktops', '- Tall, nine-foot ceilings', '- Ceramic tile flooring', 'Community Amenities', '- Secure indoor bike storage room', '- Lobby and living room area with a bar, seating, and TV', '- Beautiful views of the Berkeley Hills and San Francisco', '- Landscaped courtyard featuring native and adaptive plants', '- Bocce ball court', '- Rooftop deck', '- On-demand yoga', '- Bike maintenance station', '- Fitness room', '- Car matrix parking', '- EV charging stations', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Friendly', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday: 11:00AM-5:00PM', 'Higby', '3015 San Pablo Ave, Berkeley, CA, 94702', 'jC09NbUNeCURegular Price $3087']
